info.author: Vincent Besanceney
classifiers: Operating System :: Microsoft :: Windows :: Windows NT/2000
Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Python Modules
info.description:
Pymultitool is a Python extension that provides a high-level interface to IBM
Rational ClearCase MultiSite, suitable for scripting solutions. Pymultitool
links directly against ClearCase libraries, saving you from the extra processing
usually encountered in scripts that interact with ClearCase MultiSite, where the
creation of a multitool subprocess is required to handle a request.
